Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.37,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{That evening, it was weirdly hot.}Đêm đó khá là nóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:58.23,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{There was no breeze at all. \NJust an overall creepy night.}Không có một cơn gió và là một đêm đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.70,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{And when I glanced upward at random...}Và khi tôi nhìn lên trời...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.52,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{There was a bra flying in the sky!}Có một cái áo ngực bay phấp phới.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.50,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{You can imagine how shocked I was!}Tôi đã hết cả hồn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:15.20,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{And as disturbing a sight \Nas it was, I jumped after it!}Và lo ngại cảnh tượng đó nên đã đuổi theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:20.84,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{But when I caught it, I got the \Nfeeling someone was watching me.}Nhưng khi lấy được nó, tôi\N cảm nhận được ai đó đang quan sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.47,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{So, despite being creeped out the entire time...}Cảm giác rất là ghê rợn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:27.24,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{I cast my gaze downward.}Tôi nhìn xuống bất giác.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:34.72,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{And there he was! Between \Nthe apartment and the wall!}Và là hắn! Ở giữa căn hộ và bức tường bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:39.98,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{He was white as a sheet, and staring \Nat me with his eyes wide open!}Một tên trắng bệch và mắt mở to nhìn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.60,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{It was the ghost of a little boy!}Là hồn ma của một thằng bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:48.28,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I think that was probably just some \Nfreshly pubescent neighborhood kid}Có lẽ chỉ là một đứa\N nhóc hàng xóm mới dậy thì thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.38,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{who was flying a drone, actually.}Và nó sử dụng drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.76,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{He's been peeping on Kawado-san's \Nroom pretty regularly.}Hẳn là nó thường nhìn trộm phòng chị Kawado.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.61,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I guess he's upgraded to stealing underwear.}Và giờ là ăn trộm đồ lót.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:01.74,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Don't you think that's the kind of thing \Nyou should tell Kawado-san?!}Cậu nên nói cho Kawado về chuyện đó chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:06.63,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{More importantly, if you'd explained what \Nhappened and returned the bra to Kawado-san,}Quan trọng hơn, nếu giải \Nthích và trả lại chị ấy đồ lót,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.56,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{wouldn't that have avoided any issues?}sẽ không còn vấn đề gì cả mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:15.88,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Th-The thing is... I rushed \Ninside my room, terrified.}V-Vấn đề là... tôi hoảng quá nên chạy vội về phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.64,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{And then I suddenly felt nauseous... \Nand the bra was there, so...}Rồi thấy buồn nôn và cái áo ngực trên tay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:27.07,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{Now, I did take it to the laundromat \Nto clean it the next day!}Không, không, hôm sau tôi mang đi giặt luôn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:31.83,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{But I realized... Wouldn't it be even \Nweirder if I returned it freshly washed?}Nhưng tôi nhận ra... giặt xong trả lại thì có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.87,Flashback,Ono,0,0,0,,{So I've been unable to give it back...}Nên đã không thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:39.40,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Ono-san... That doesn't explain \Nwhy you're wearing it, though.}Anh Ono à... thế còn lý do anh mặc nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.33,Signs,Graffiti 2,0,0,0,,{\c&H1E2531&\pos(320,36.667)}{I want to be a ninja}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.55,FlashbackItalicsTop,News,0,0,0,,{Last night, a man was assaulted \Non the street in 2-chome}Đêm qua, một vụ giết người ở khu 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:52.08,FlashbackItalicsTop,News,0,0,0,,{in Nerima Ward's Koinu neighborhood.}ở quận Nerima khu Koinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.98,FlashbackItalicsTop,News,0,0,0,,{The victim was seriously injured,}Nạn nhân bị thương nặng,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.60,FlashbackItalicsTop,News,0,0,0,,{and the police are treating the \Nincident as randomly targeted.}và cảnh sát cho rằng sát nhân chỉ nhắm bừa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.72,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{So tired...}Mệt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.23,FlashbackItalicsTop,News,0,0,0,,{And now, our next story.}Và tin tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.51,Flashback,Kawado,0,0,0,,{That's close by.}Gần khu mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:09.10,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\an2\pos(320,305)\bord1}{Late July 24th}24/7 đêm khuya
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:11.35,FlashbackTop,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Not getting a lot of pressure \Nout of my stream tonight...}Cũng không áp lực lắm\N cho buổi phát sóng trực tiếp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:17.54,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Despite it being for a mission, he was \Nreluctant to grab another man's organ.}Dù là vì nhiệm vụ, nhưng hắn không \Nngần ngại ra tay với người tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:23.75,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Thus, he would think back to the oden \Nhe had eaten on his first day in Japan,}Trong khi đó hắn vẫn nghĩ về món \Noden lần đầu được ăn ở Nhật.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:26.06,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{in order to better execute his task.}Để có thể hoàn thành nhiệm vụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:30.70,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{By imagining the penis as a \Nfried tofu pouch wiener roll,}Bằng cách tưởng tượng thứ đó\Nlà cuốn đậu hũ chiên,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.34,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{he was able to dull his sense of revulsion...}hắn đã có thể làm dịu đi cảm giác bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:37.38,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{But he soon realized his mistake.}Nhưng hắn đã sớm nhận ra sai lầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:42.80,Narration,Narrator,0,0,0,,{The shaft that he had been imagining as a \Npiece of oden... was actually a piece of oden.}Sự tưởng tượng của hắn\N về oden... hoá ra là oden thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.14,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{He'll get behind me!}Hắn ở phía sau mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:47.39,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Or not?!}Hoặc không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.28,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Not moving the way I'd like to...}Cơ thể nặng nề thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.12,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{A ninja.}Ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.60,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I thought I would need three dicks, but...}Cứ nghĩ phải cần đến 3 con cu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.79,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I've managed to make contact.}mới có thể gặp được.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.31,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{What is this feeling of elation?}Cảm giác phấn khích này là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.80,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Is it the joy of getting to fight a member \Nof the world's greatest league of killers?}Có phải niềm vui khi được chiến đấu với\N thành viên băng sát thủ hùng mạnh nhất không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.92,FlashbackItalics,Sasama,0,0,0,,{A karambit knife? \NSome Russian assassin, then?}Dao karambit? Sát thủ từ Nga à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.18,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{For a moment... even \Nif it was just a moment...}Trong khoảnh khoắc, chỉ trong khoảnh khắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:27.42,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{That thrill was stronger than \Nmy dedication to my daughter!}Mình đã quên đi sự khao khát cứu con gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:17.40,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I need to be cautious of \Nthose tricky ninja moves.}Phải cẩn thận với chiêu trò của ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:22.53,FlashbackItalics,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Gotta think of him as moving \Nin 3D, not just on a plane.}Phải nghĩ hắn đang di chuyển trong không gian 3D.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.80,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,Om anichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.05,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,Marishiei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.22,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,Sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.43,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{He vanished?!}Hắn biến mất?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.44,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{But just the torso?!}Nhưng chỉ phần trên?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.83,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{That must be ninjutsu...}Có vẻ là nhẫn thuật...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.07,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{A camouflage technique, maybe.}Kĩ năng nguỵ trang...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.96,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{My attacks amounted to nothing...}Các đòn tấn công vô dụng với hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.66,DefaultTop,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Ninja live up to their reputation.}Ninja quả xứng với cái tên.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:21.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\an2\pos(320,305)\bord1}{The same day, 8 hours prior}8 tiếng trước
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:24.26,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'm not getting much from wearing this.}Mặc vào cũng không thể đồng cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.69,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Bras really are more fun to take \Noff someone else than wear yourself.}Quả nhiên áo ngực phải cởi của gái mới thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:33.80,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Y'know, I've never had the desire \Nto steal one before...}Với cả trước giờ mình chưa từng \Ncó hứng đi ăn trộm thứ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:37.38,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Yet, once Ono-san was gone, I had the \Nurge to grab this without asking him.}Anh Ono đang ra ngoài,\N mình đã tự tiện lấy mà không xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.60,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Is it just their inherent charm?}Mị lực của áo ngực à...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.36,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{You seem bored.}Rảnh nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.73,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{And you talk to yourself. A lot.}Cậu thích nói chuyện một mình nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.54,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{You haven't spilled any classified \Ninformation like that, have you?}Chưa tiết lộ thông tin quan trọng gì phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.25,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Of course not!}Dĩ nhiên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.13,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{This is just... rehearsing \Nthe kind of act to put on}Đây chỉ là... em đang diễn tập hành động
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.84,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{when I want to play a weirdo \Nthat people want distance from.}khi đóng vai kẻ lập dị làm mọi người né tránh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:08.56,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{So that hoodie was inside the \Npackage I gave you last time?}Cái áo đó nằm trong gói hàng đợt trước nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:13.01,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Oh, right. Along with a high school uniform...}À vâng, cùng với đồng phục...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.51,FlashbackItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,{Looks like it's blade-proof and bulletproof.}Có vẻ nó chống dao và chống đạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.02,Signs,Label,0,0,0,,{\pos(326.667,210.667)\an5\b0\fs12\c&H41342A&\3c&H92857C&\bord1\frz83.19\frx354\fry316}{Marishiten}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.38,FlashbackItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,Marishiten 4.0?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.55,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{So... want anything to drink?}Thế... em mang trà ra nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.40,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{I'm not in the mood to be served \Ndrinks by someone dressed like you.}Nhìn cái bộ dạng cậu là tôi hết muốn uống rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.41,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{I want an update on the progress of your job.}Tôi đến nghe tiến độ công việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.53,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.57,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{After opening the package I received,}Sau khi nhận gói hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.71,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I discerned that the mission was \Nto infiltrate a high school...}Em nhận ra nhiệm vụ là\N xâm nhập vào trường cấp 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:46.54,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{So I've been on standby at home until \Nthe entrance exam, which is this Saturday.}Nên đã ở nhà chờ kì thi tuyển diễn ra vào thứ 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.19,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{I see. That means you've got \Nthree days of free time, then?}Vậy à. Còn 3 ngày rảnh rỗi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.80,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Have you heard of the Nerima Slasher?}Đã nghe về máy chém Nerima chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.93,Flashback,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Yeah, from the web. \NSomething about dicks getting cut off?}Vâng. Trên mạng... Là một tên cắt cu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.06,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Your job...}Công việc đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:02.52,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{is to dispose of him within three days.}Xoá sổ hắn trong vòng 3 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:12.27,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{That career ninja froze for a \Nsecond when he saw the hoodie.}Tên ninja đó như đứng \Nhình khi anh ta thấy chiếc áo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.67,FlashbackItalics,Kuro,0,0,0,,{There must be something more to it.}Cái này phải có gì nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:25.81,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Om anichi marishiei sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:32.93,Default,Mako,0,0,0,,{Ridiculous. Is that the \Nlatest Marishiten model?}Nực cườ, đó là mẫu mới nhất của Marishiten à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.66,Default,Mako,0,0,0,,{The Metro PD's leaks were accurate.}Thông tin rò rỉ từ Metro là chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.72,Default,Mako,0,0,0,,{It only conceals the upper body, \Nwith the rest being clear as day.}Nó chỉ có thể nguỵ trang phần trên.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.81,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Say, Ozu...}Nè Ozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.48,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You ever seen a Marishisten 4.0?}Anh từng thấy Marishiten 4.0 chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.08,Default,Ozu,0,0,0,,{No. Don't they only go \Nto front-line operators?}Chưa. Cái đó là sản phẩm mới nhất mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.38,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You'd think so.}Thế à.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.70,DefaultItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,{Sasama-san was hinting \Nabout this on that day...}Sasama đã ám chỉ điều này vào hôm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.05,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1350)\fnArial Black\fs40\pos(321.6,21.2)\c&H313433&}{September 9th}9/9 12h47
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(607,976)\fnArial Black\fs40\pos(321.6,21.2)\c&H313433&}{July 25th}30/7 9h14
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.73,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Blue hoodie...}Áo hoodie xanh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:30.60,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{A foreigner with blond hair and glasses...}Người ngoại quốc với tóc vàng đeo kính...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.74,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{In a blue hoodie...}mặc áo hoodie xanh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:35.54,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Whatcha looking for?}Tìm gì đấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.99,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{None of your business, Mr. Breast Milk!}Liên quan gì tới ông!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:40.37,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{You been eating properly?}Dạo này có ăn uống đàng hoàng không đấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.37,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Sure have. Steak, and pasta \NNapolitan, and fried oysters...}Dĩ nhiên. Bít tết, mì ý, hàu chiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.29,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{But the thing is, I'm on a diet.}Nhưng mà cháu đang ăn kiêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.75,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{A diet?}Ăn kiêng?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.63,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Little kids gotta eat, drink, and poop plenty!}Trẻ em phải ăn uống ỉa đái đầy đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.42,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Here, have some breast milk!}Đây, uống sữa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.89,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Ew, there it is! The breast milk!}Gớm quá! Lão sữa mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.47,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{So a kid is looking for the foreigner...}Nó đang tìm tên ngoại quốc à...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.54,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{But on whose orders?}Nhưng lệnh từ kẻ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.40,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Blue hoodie, blond with glasses...}Áo Hoodie xanh, tóc vàng đeo kính...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.86,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{I found the foreigner!}Đã tìm thấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.28,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Now he'll let me borrow the drone!}Giờ thì anh ấy sẽ cho mình mượn drone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.79,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Are you a ninja?}Nhóc là ninja à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.64,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{I'm not a ninja. I'm playing hide-and-seek.}Không phải ninja, đang chơi trốn tìm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.14,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Hide and... seek?}Trốn tìm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.80,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{I found you, Mr. Foreigner, so you lose!}Đã tìm thấy chú ngoại quốc, thua rồi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.82,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I lost?}Ta thua?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:42.31,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Yes, I have indeed lost. I even used a gun...}Đúng là ta đã thua... dù đã sử dụng súng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:46.30,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{But I wasn't able to defeat \Na ninja in urban combat.}Nhưng vẫn không thể đánh bại một ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.69,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Could you please bring me \Nmy matsugo no mizu?}Nếu được có thể mang cho ta\N matsugo no mizu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:53.43,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{What the heck is that? \NSome water from Matsuko?}Là cái gì? Nước từ Matsuko hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:57.31,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{No, it's... a last drink of water before dying.}Không, ngụm nước cuối cùng trước khi chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.79,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Sure, here you go.}Rồi, có đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.83,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I feel alive again.}Cảm giác sống lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.58,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Dying and reviving! You sure keep busy.}Chết đi và sống lại! Chú bận rộn ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:14.59,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{How old are you?}Nhóc mấy tuổi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.40,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{I'm ten.}10.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.84,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Ten years old...}10 tuổi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.73,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{My daughter was just born recently.}Con gái ta vừa mới sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:27.90,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{I wanted to watch her grow up.}Ta muốn bên cạnh nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.85,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{But... I doubt I'll ever see her again.}Nhưng có lẽ... sẽ không gặp lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.60,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:36.06,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Because I failed my mission.}Vì ta đã thất bại.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.45,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{The ninja won't let me escape...}Ninja sẽ không để ta thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:43.30,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{And my employers won't forgive my failure.}Và đồng đội cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.24,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{But why?! Come on! It'll be okay!}Nhưng tại sao? Mọi chuyện sẽ ổn thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.00,Flashback,Junna,0,0,0,,{Just leave it to me!}Cứ để cháu lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:55.21,Flashback,Foreigner,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you, but... \Nplease don't shake the shrine.}C-Cảm ơn nhưng... đừng phá đền thờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.51,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{It's good to see you again, Sasama-san.}Đã lâu không gặp, anh Sasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:04.34,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Kato... Want some breast milk?}Kato... muốn uống sữa mẹ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.64,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{No, thank you.}Không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.02,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Sasama-san...}Anh Sasama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.27,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Why did you step down?}Sao anh lại rút lui?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:18.14,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{The fighting in Timbuktu was nasty.}Trận chiến ở Timbuktu quá nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:22.15,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Surrounded on all sides, \Nkilometers deep. Nowhere to run.}Bao vây tứ phía, không còn đường lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:28.41,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Kato, you're one of the few \Npeople I trust to watch my back.}Kato, cậu là một trong số ít người tôi tin tưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.91,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{I thought having you guys at my back \Nwould let me move forward,}Tôi nghĩ cậu sẽ ở sau lưng và thúc tôi tiến bước.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.96,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{so I opened the doors in front of me.}Để tôi có thể mở cánh cửa đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:42.22,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{I kept doing that, and after every door, \Nthere were only more doors. Never an exit.}Và cứ thế mở hết cánh cửa này \Ntới cánh cửa khác, không có lối thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.43,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{It was depressing, Kato.}Tôi đã rất thất vọng, Kato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.02,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Have some breast milk. It's nutritious.}Đây, uống sữa đi. Dinh dưỡng lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.88,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{Is this your way of criticizing \Nthe organization?}Đây là cách anh phản đối tổ chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.63,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,{First Class Ninja Sasama.}Ninja hạng 1, Sasama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.11,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Former, actually.}Đã từng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.99,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{It's been seventy years \Nsince the war ended,}Đã 70 năm chiến tranh kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:09.62,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{but the Prime Minister still hasn't made \Nuse of his priority command over us.}Nhưng nội các vẫn ra lệnh \Nưu tiên quyền hạn cho chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:14.79,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{There are 290,000 police officers, \N230,000 JSDF officers,}Có 290.000 cảnh sát, 230.000 JFDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:18.54,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{and 200,000 of us.}Và 200.000 ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:22.18,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{So how is it that over 90% \Nof our numbers are in Japan?}Và tại sao 90% trong số đó còn ở Nhật Bản?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:27.72,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Why is it that the top of the Chunin class \Nhave been recalled from overseas duty,}Tại sao những người đứng đầu lớp Chunin \Nlại bị loại bỏ khỏi nhiệm vụ quốc tế?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.81,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{and stuck working on missions \Ninside our borders?}Và mắc kẹt bởi những nhiệm vụ trong nước?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:38.01,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Why is a militarized organization of our size \Nnot under civilian control by the government?}Tại sao tổ chức quân sự to lớn như chúng ta\N không nằm dưới sự kiểm soát của chính phủ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:40.46,Flashback,Kato,0,0,0,,UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:45.57,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,{Exactly. All of these questions \Nlead to the same thing.}Chính xác. Tất cả bí ẩn đều dẫn đến một.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:55.37,Flashback,Sasama,0,0,0,,Under Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.48,FlashbackItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,Bỏ trốn rồi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:08.68,FlashbackItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,{But things are starting to get dicey...}Nhưng mọi chuyện bắt đầu phiền phức rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:15.10,Default,Ozu,0,0,0,,{Something wrong, Kato?}Có gì sao, Kato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:20.09,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{No... It's nothing.}Không, không có gì.
