Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:58.83,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Ono is apparently the 70th most \Ncommon family name in Japan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:02.32,DefaultTop,Ono,0,0,0,,{That's so half-assed... \NMakes me wanna say, "Oh, no!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:04.70,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Wow. That was annoying. \NI think I'll tell her about the bra.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.67,DefaultTop,Ono,0,0,0,,{Please, not that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.26,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{See, that was when you \Nshould've said, "Oh, no!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:09.58,DefaultTop,Ono,0,0,0,,{You're a funny guy.}
